Password Management System 
Module:-
1.Register user(send mail only -> next version to Send Mail  user to confirmation )
  a).forgot password(using to routs->next version to using html template)
  b).Edit users details
  c).view users details
  d).Delete users profile(next version->deactivate account)
  e).Reset Password
2.Login User
3.Password:-Category Like-
   1).Software Passwords(Godaddy Password, Wordpress),
   2). Social Profile(Facebook,Twitter,...), 
   3).Banking Profile(SBI Banking, HDFC NET Banking, Atm pin..)
4.Manage password like:Edit,Delete,view
5.Add Nominee of users 
Nominee Details(Model):-
   Name
   Gender
   Phone
   email
   Nominee Relation
   Rank/priority of Nominee[ choose from three option:1st, 2nd 3rd]/allocation in percentage from 100 minium three nominee required this section is editable according user preference
   Date of Birth/Age
   Signature
   Identity Documents(minimum required one from voter id , pan, aadhar card)
   Address